Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.05,0:07:21.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正常进行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.98,0:07:23.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要乱来啊 咲良
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.89,0:07:25.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直接正式上场
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.31,0:07:27.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然对不起羽佐间老师他们 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.30,0:07:28.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弄坏了我也在所不惜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.92,0:07:30.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.08,0:07:33.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这感觉真是久违了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.16,0:07:36.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是变性意识 不要被自己的心灵吞噬了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.21,0:07:39.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就担心自己吧 出动了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.41,0:07:55.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是骑兵模型
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.01,0:07:57.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天照 诱敌成功
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.20,0:08:00.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,展开护盾 形成战场
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.06,0:08:02.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fafner部队 出击
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.97,0:08:04.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迅速歼灭敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.30,0:08:12.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十三号机的机库无应答
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.67,0:08:14.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机体无异常 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.56,0:08:15.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 卡诺恩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.83,0:08:23.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.34,0:08:27.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在看到的是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.04,0:08:39.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再怎么困 只要驾驶Fafner就会清醒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.17,0:08:40.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道要我不要下去？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.24,0:08:44.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看那里 是咲良学姐的三号机
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.14,0:08:48.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师 真的来陪我们作战了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.00,0:08:51.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无人机…能用吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.95,0:08:54.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人分散 全体准备迎击
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.73,0:08:58.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 在海里同化能力减半
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.39,0:09:01.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要同化岛只能从空中来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.71,0:09:04.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们只能乖乖上我们的战场 Festum
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.21,0:09:07.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咲良 冷静
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.61,0:09:08.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,专心支援
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.23,0:09:10.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.71,0:09:12.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.09,0:09:39.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fafner部队 接敌
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.17,0:09:43.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,格纳库发来报告 十三号机启动发生故障
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.84,0:09:45.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能出击吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.99,0:09:49.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 她只是不能理解力量而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.40,0:09:50.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,力量？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.65,0:09:53.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种力量一直在等待萌芽
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.31,0:09:55.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接受祝福吧 卡诺恩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.08,0:09:57.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了岛和世界
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.60,0:10:04.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重新启动
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.05,0:10:08.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.54,0:10:10.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是哪里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.59,0:10:16.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mk.Sein？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.71,0:10:31.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重新启动
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.33,0:10:40.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,侵入龙宫岛本岛了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.71,0:10:44.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在记录数据
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.43,0:10:45.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,几时开始的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.50,0:10:47.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.87,0:10:52.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,显示当前时间
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.92,0:10:54.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和刚才的时间不同
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.85,0:10:56.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 时间倒转了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.17,0:11:00.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间…不同的时间…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.10,0:11:04.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,显示记录数据一览表
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.63,0:11:10.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都是今后的时间？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.87,0:11:11.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未来的…
