Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.31,0:21:33.09,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}蜷身抱住双膝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.11,0:21:38.57,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}藏起泪水不让人看见
