Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.38,0:23:00.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巧克力？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.54,0:23:02.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.99,0:23:07.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.39,0:23:10.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真壁司令 远见老师
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.39,0:23:12.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剑司 咲良
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.14,0:23:17.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,九号机… 
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.60,0:23:18.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里奈！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.29,0:23:47.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你即将知晓
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.49,0:23:53.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的悲剧 并非诞生于绝望
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.45,0:23:57.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与命运抗争而找到的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.96,0:24:01.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是它驱使我们走上牺牲之途
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.79,0:24:08.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苍穹之Fafner EXODUS
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.90,0:24:10.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在那里吗
